{"pageNumber":586,"juzNumber":30,"verses":[{"key":"81:1","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":1,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ إِذَا ٱلشَّمْسُ كُوِّرَتْ","translationText":"When the sun is wrapped up [in darkness]"},{"key":"81:2","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":2,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ ٱنكَدَرَتْ","translationText":"And when the stars fall, dispersing,"},{"key":"81:3","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":3,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَإِذَا ٱلْجِبَالُ سُيِّرَتْ","translationText":"And when the mountains are removed"},{"key":"81:4","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":4,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَإِذَا ٱلْعِشَارُ عُطِّلَتْ","translationText":"And when full-term she-camels are neglected"},{"key":"81:5","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":5,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَإِذَا ٱلْوُحُوشُ حُشِرَتْ","translationText":"And when the wild beasts are gathered"},{"key":"81:6","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":6,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَإِذَا ٱلْبِحَارُ سُجِّرَتْ","translationText":"And when the seas are filled with flame"},{"key":"81:7","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":7,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّفُوسُ زُوِّجَتْ","translationText":"And when the souls are paired"},{"key":"81:8","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":8,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَإِذَا ٱلْمَوْءُۥدَةُ سُئِلَتْ","translationText":"And when the girl [who was] buried alive is asked"},{"key":"81:9","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":9,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"بِأَىِّ ذَنۢبٍۢ قُتِلَتْ","translationText":"For what sin she was killed"},{"key":"81:10","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":10,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَإِذَا ٱلصُّحُفُ نُشِرَتْ","translationText":"And when the pages are made public"},{"key":"81:11","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":11,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ كُشِطَتْ","translationText":"And when the sky is stripped away"},{"key":"81:12","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":12,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَإِذَا ٱلْجَحِيمُ سُعِّرَتْ","translationText":"And when Hellfire is set ablaze"},{"key":"81:13","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":13,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَإِذَا ٱلْجَنَّةُ أُزْلِفَتْ","translationText":"And when Paradise is brought near,"},{"key":"81:14","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":14,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"عَلِمَتْ نَفْسٌۭ مَّآ أَحْضَرَتْ","translationText":"A soul will [then] know what it has brought [with it]."},{"key":"81:15","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":15,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"فَلَآ أُقْسِمُ بِٱلْخُنَّسِ","translationText":"So I swear by the retreating stars -"},{"key":"81:16","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":16,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"ٱلْجَوَارِ ٱلْكُنَّسِ","translationText":"Those that run [their courses] and disappear -"},{"key":"81:17","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":17,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَٱلَّيْلِ إِذَا عَسْعَسَ","translationText":"And by the night as it closes in"},{"key":"81:18","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":18,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَٱلصُّبْحِ إِذَا تَنَفَّسَ","translationText":"And by the dawn when it breathes"},{"key":"81:19","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":19,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوْلُ رَسُولٍۢ كَرِيمٍۢ","translationText":"[That] indeed, the Qur'an is a word [conveyed by] a noble messenger"},{"key":"81:20","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":20,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"ذِى قُوَّةٍ عِندَ ذِى ٱلْعَرْشِ مَكِينٍۢ","translationText":"[Who is] possessed of power and with the Owner of the Throne, secure [in position],"},{"key":"81:21","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":21,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"مُّطَاعٍۢ ثَمَّ أَمِينٍۢ","translationText":"Obeyed there [in the heavens] and trustworthy."},{"key":"81:22","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":22,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَمَا صَاحِبُكُم بِمَجْنُونٍۢ","translationText":"And your companion is not [at all] mad."},{"key":"81:23","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":23,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَلَقَدْ رَءَاهُ بِٱلْأُفُقِ ٱلْمُبِينِ","translationText":"And he has already seen Gabriel in the clear horizon."},{"key":"81:24","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":24,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَمَا هُوَ عَلَى ٱلْغَيْبِ بِضَنِينٍۢ","translationText":"And Muhammad is not a withholder of [knowledge of] the unseen."},{"key":"81:25","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":25,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَمَا هُوَ بِقَوْلِ شَيْطَٰنٍۢ رَّجِيمٍۢ","translationText":"And the Qur'an is not the word of a devil, expelled [from the heavens]."},{"key":"81:26","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":26,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"فَأَيْنَ تَذْهَبُونَ","translationText":"So where are you going?"},{"key":"81:27","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":27,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"إِنْ هُوَ إِلَّا ذِكْرٌۭ لِّلْعَٰلَمِينَ","translationText":"It is not except a reminder to the worlds"},{"key":"81:28","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":28,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"لِمَن شَآءَ مِنكُمْ أَن يَسْتَقِيمَ","translationText":"For whoever wills among you to take a right course."},{"key":"81:29","surahNumber":81,"ayahNumber":29,"juzNumber":30,"pageNumber":586,"arabicText":"وَمَا تَشَآءُونَ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُ رَبُّ ٱلْعَٰلَمِينَ","translationText":"And you do not will except that Allah wills - Lord of the worlds."}],"translationEditionUsed":"en.sahih"}